      <title>部长表示南非停电将在周三缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-11/south-africa-blackouts-what-s-behind-the-latest-severe-outages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非电力部长表示，随着受影响的机组恢复供电，南非不断升级的停电应该会在周中逐渐减少。]]></description>
